    "body": "I have more fixes that I will PR later on.\r\n\r\nI think we should also change the API to something like this for greater flexibility:\r\n\r\n```js\r\ncustomWindowButtons: {\r\n  x: 0,\r\n  y: 0,\r\n  showOnHover: true,\r\n}\r\n```\r\n\r\n`titleBarStyle: 'hidden' | 'hidden-inset'` would then be deprecated and mapped to `customWindowButtons` for backwards compatibility.\r\n\r\n@mst128256 @tonyganch Thoughts?"
