    "body": "@MarshallOfSound The rectangular window is caused by: https://github.com/electron/electron/blob/7a3a092c720c66090898df8d1547fc89017d0d5b/atom/browser/native_window_mac.mm#L843-L847\r\n\r\nI was going to remove it in this PR, but it made the window buttons always visible. I'm planning to change our custom window button implementation to no longer rely on it and then get rid of it in a future PR. Maybe we should have a separate option to use `NSFullSizeContentViewWindowMask`."
